Title: Got the Babysitter Pregnant
Plot: A young Earl gets his heart broken by the babysitter and swears revenge on her and her boyfriend. Now, Earl is older and wiser, so he decides to cross them off his list, but it may have terrible repercussions for Randy. Meanwhile, Joy loses Darnell's pet turtle
Writer: Vali Chandrasekaran, Patrick McCarthy, Erika Kaestle
GuestStars: Adam Rose, Brie Gabrielle, Michael Nardelli
